data.description: Discover your exquisite urban sanctuary nestled in the vibrant heart of Atlanta's Edgewood. This corner lot home, fully renovated from top to bottom, offers a seamless blend of luxury and convenience. Revel in the custom hardwood floors that grace every corner, creating an open-concept living space perfect for hosting guests. Indulge in the remodeled kitchen, boasting quartz countertops and high-end stainless appliances, accompanied by a dedicated laundry space. The expansive primary suite serves as a tranquil retreat, featuring an updated en-suite with a soaking tub, a spacious walk-in closet, and French doors leading to the patio. With three additional generously-sized bedrooms and two fully updated guest bathrooms, this home caters to families and those in need of a remote office. Maintenance is a breeze with two utility closets, and peace of mind comes from knowing the HVAC/AC and water heater are just a year old. The property, equipped with up-to-date underground utilities, also provides space for future expansion. Included are construction plans for enthusiasts interested in adding a second floor. Positioned in the heart of Edgewood, steps away from the Beltline and renowned restaurants like El Tesoro and Chop Shop, this home offers easy access to the highway, Little Five Points, and East Atlanta. As a bonus, utilizing our preferred lender, Whitney Owings with Supreme Lending, could result in a contribution of up to $4,000 towards closing costs. Seize this opportunity to own a genuine oasis in the heart of Atlanta's most dynamic neighborhood!
